snippet.title: AirStrike 3D: Operation W.A.T. (PC) - Gameplay | No Commentary
snippet.description:
AirStrike 3D is vertically-scrolling shooter featuring a single helicopter. The game world is fully in 3-D and can be played at a slanted 3-D angle or a more traditional "top-view".
